review_blob: This is a great tasting wheat beer.  It is as smooth as a wheat beer should be and has an amazing ale taste which is what makes or breaks the hefeweizen beer for me.  This one rates up their with boulevard and sierra Nevada to me.

beer_brewer_name: Leinenkugel Brewing Company (Tenth & Blake Beer Co.)
review_blob: Not a bad beer by any means, despite the reviews.  Ive not drank many kolsch style beers however I do think this is a tasty beer and enjoy the slight rye taste.
Very good rye pa.  Great earthy aroma and an amazing hoppy taste.  Best rye pa I have had to date
Coming from a company whose known for their soda this is a decent beer.  However, the beer is over powered by the creek water taste.
One of the best hefeweizen beers I have had.  This beer has a fruity after taste that is just like the bottle proclaims "reminiscent of ripe banana".
What beer should be. A great tasting ale beer with a hoppy taste and a nutty after taste.
Best way I can describe this beer is its a very good american pale ale with a piney taste that is very overpowering.  Dont get me wrong its a great beer though.
Very smooth medium beer.  Has a cinnamon fruity taste that blends perfect with the beer.
Great pilsner but nothing spectacular which is what Ive came to expect from the boulevard smokestack series.
beer_name: Boulevard Smokestack Series - Reverb Imperial Pilsner

review_blob: Im not particularly impressed with shock top beers after all they are a mega brewery craft beer.  I do really like this beer though it has an extreme taste that Ive yet to find anywhere else.  You got the full flavor of an IPA with the smoothness of a wheat beer.
Reminds me a lot of tank 7 without the fruity after taste.  This smokestack beer has very smooth taste that makes you want to take another drink.
beer_name: Boulevard Smokestack Series - Harvest Dance Wheat Wine

review_blob: Boulevard brewing company is my favorite micro brewery but this is probably my least favorite of their beers.  Having said that it is very good, great taste but this beer just wasnt on the level of the other boulevards.
Very tasty fall beer.  Full flavored octoberfest style beer with a hint of nutty flavor.  Perfect for an October night.....or day.
If youre looking for a stout you can not go wrong with this beer.  Perfect smokey taste.
beer_name: Boulevard Smokestack Series - Dark Truth Stout

review_blob: Very impressed with this unconvential wheat beer.  It has a very strong peach taste but its a nice change.
Very potent (over 10% alcohol content) but a very good beer.  Its a stronger beer that doesnt taste like a stronger beer.  Good ale taste with hint of fruit (fig and date)
beer_name: Boulevard Smokestack Series - The Sixth Glass Quadrupel

review_blob: A great tasting ale.  It has a great smell, sweet taste.  Probably the best beer Ive ever had.
beer_name: Boulevard Smokestack Series - Tank 7 Farmhouse Ale

review_blob: Its an APA but theres nothing particularly special about this APA.  Its not a bad beer but theres nothing that stands out to separate this from the others.
A good fall beer that tastes like a combination of pumpkin cookies and a quality beer.
Marvelous white beer.  Perfect beer for a sunny summer day.  Great diverse taste.  Another quality boulevard beer.

You can not go wrong with this IPA.  Great hippy taste.  You can tell boulevard uses quality ingredients
.
Absolutely the best pilsner you will ever drink.  Everything down to the bottle is perfect.
A nice marzen style ale.  The few I have had tasted a little bland from what I expected but may have been due to beer age
This is a very tasty wheat ipa.  It has the taste youd expect from an ipa and the smoothness youd expect from a wheat beer.
This is my favorite craft beer.  Its a very smooth wheat beer that is great bottled and even better on draft.
